GetPalette Documentation

RadGEEToolbox.GetPalette.get_palette(name)

Returns the color palette associated with the given name.

Args: name: options: ‘algae’, ‘dense’, ‘greens’, ‘haline’, ‘inferno’, ‘jet’, ‘matter’, ‘pubu’, ‘soft_blue_green_red’, ‘thermal’, ‘turbid’, ‘ylord’

Returns: list: list of colors to be used for image visualization in GEE vis params
